title: GIP 2-Modify Farming Rewards
body:
Cut rewards for all pools by 70% for the remainder of farming except for pools: uni-v2 gds/eth and staking gds pools. Distribute rewards reduced from other pools to uni-v2 gds/eth and staking gds at the rate of 60/40 respectively. 

Remove farming of fragments from all pools except staking gds pool. Distribute fragment rewards reduced from other pools to staking gds pool.
author: 0xAb30f11201d6D53215729D45DC05a0966C237922
